column9: 'Sample structure showing the different element types.'
column10:
'<?xml version="1.0"?>

<root> 
  <dynamic-element name="sample-text" type="text"/>  
  <dynamic-element name="sample-text-box" type="text_box"/>  
  <dynamic-element name="sample-text-area" type="text_area"/>  
  <dynamic-element name="sample-image" type="image"/>  
  <dynamic-element name="sample-boolean-flag" type="boolean"/>  
  <dynamic-element name="sample-selection-list" type="list"> 
    <dynamic-element name="coke" type="Coke"></dynamic-element>  
    <dynamic-element name="pepsi" type="Pepsi"/> 
  </dynamic-element>  
  <dynamic-element name="sample-multi-selection-list" type="multi-list"> 
    <dynamic-element name="chocolate" type="Chocolate"></dynamic-element>  
    <dynamic-element name="strawberry" type="Strawberry"></dynamic-element>  
    <dynamic-element name="vanilla" type="Vanilla"/> 
  </dynamic-element> 
</root>'
